text: Tápiószentmárton is a village in Pest county, Hungary. == Locate == It can be approached by the main road no. 4. The most practical way to get there is using the Budapest-Újszász-Szolnok train line. Travel to Nagykáta, then with bus. Tápiószentmárton has its own train station, but it is far away from the central. == References == Category:Populated places in Pest County
title: Tápiószentmárton
